---
// Modern Security Notice Component
---

<div class="security-notice">
  <div class="notice-icon">
    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/>
      <path d="M8 11l2 2 4-4"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="notice-content">
    <h3 class="notice-title">Security First Architecture</h3>
    <p class="notice-description">
      Direct trading from frontend is disabled for security. All trading operations must go through 
      authenticated GitHub Actions workflows with proper API key validation.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .security-notice {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    background: hsl(var(--warning) / 0.05);
    border: 1px solid hsl(var(--warning) / 0.2);
    border-left: 4px solid hsl(var(--warning));
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  
  .notice-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: hsl(var(--warning) / 0.1);
    color: hsl(var(--warning));
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .notice-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  
  .notice-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: hsl(var(--warning));
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-sm) 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }
  
  .notice-description {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .security-notice {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
    }
    
    .notice-icon {
      align-self: center;
    }
    
    .notice-title {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }
    
    .notice-description {
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
    }
  }
</style> 